\name
wall - display the wall or add an entry
\synopsis
wall [sentence]
\description
Allows you to display the wall or add an entry in.
The displayed lines number is defined in wall_display_count.
\example
> wall all in all it's just another brick in the wall
You write to the wall: all in all it's just another brick in the wall
> wall
Wall :
20/05/2003 21:50:24 Root all in all it's just another brick in the wall
End of Wall
